  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From the twisted mind of TROMA Shorts Creator Emil Levin comes a new old-school first-person shooter paying homage to genre classics such as Blood, Duke Nukem 3D and Rise of the Triad. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>REVEREND puts you in the boots of a disillusioned former reverend, tasked with fighting back against the evil lurking beneath the church he once called home. Battle against Eldritch and Demonic beasts that would cripple the average mind to witness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Visit varied nightmarish locations ranging from crematoriums to flesh-pits. Use powerful and distinctive weaponry, including forbidden fruit which explode upon contact with the horrors surrounding you. Hunt for keys and scavenge for resources to keep you alive and get you closer to your goal. Also, keep an eye out for secrets, as easter eggs, resources and secret pathways make exploration a strong recommendation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>GRISLY ENVIRONMENTS<br>UNHOLY ARSENAL<br>GRUESOME BOSS FIGHTS<br>SATISTYING SECRETS<br>GORE, SWEET GORE<br>CLASSIC 90s FPS GAMEPLAY<br>HIDEOUS ENEMIES<br><br>Be sure to check out the old-school manual in your Steam Library Hub! Questions will be answered... and raised.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/35daed7d3deb3f6fa281a2d7ae370278.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From the twisted mind of TROMA Shorts Creator Emil Levin comes a new old-school first-person shooter paying homage to genre classics such as Blood, Duke Nukem 3D and Rise of the Triad. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/1a9e4f31b0436806fb91ff7a63139cc3.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>REVEREND puts you in the boots of a disillusioned former reverend, tasked with fighting back against the evil lurking beneath the church he once called home. Battle against Eldritch and Demonic beasts that would cripple the average mind to witness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/e6076168b5ba97038ba4ecf7b48e1bd1.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Visit varied nightmarish locations ranging from crematoriums to flesh-pits. Use powerful and distinctive weaponry, including forbidden fruit which explode upon contact with the horrors surrounding you. Hunt for keys and scavenge for resources to keep you alive and get you closer to your goal. Also, keep an eye out for secrets, as easter eggs, resources and secret pathways make exploration a strong recommendation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.poster.avif?t=1765193478\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.webm?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977570/extras/98185b804b9914f1781613d608f427d9.mp4?t=1765193478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>GRISLY ENVIRONMENTS<br>UNHOLY ARSENAL<br>GRUESOME BOSS FIGHTS<br>SATISTYING SECRETS<br>GORE, SWEET GORE<br>CLASSIC 90s FPS GAMEPLAY<br>HIDEOUS ENEMIES<br><br>Be sure to check out the old-school manual in your Steam Library Hub! Questions will be answered... and raised.",
